  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK181">
<l>aṟamkūṟā ṉalla ceyiṉu moruvaṉ</l>
<l>puṟamkūṟā ṉeṉṟa liṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though one do not even speak of virtue and live in sin, it will be well if it be said of him "he does not backbite."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
